er Docker error and prevents misleading `--run-tests --adopt-if-green` behavior. ⚠️ Weaknesses — full live validation still needs to run after install. 🔍 Unknowns — whether you want `--run-tests --adopt-if-green` to become a supported full workflow later. 🧩 Next step — install `v0.0.198`, upload/add it to Project Sources, then run: ```bash ./chatgpt_claudecode_workflow_release_control.sh \ --tests-only \ --adopt-if-green ```

