sk` does not yet automatically generate/send the full request envelope; this release focuses on schemas and reply parsing. 🔍 Unknowns — whether live ChatGPT answers consistently preserve the marked JSON envelope without formatting drift. 🧩 Next step — install/upload `v0.0.201`, then run guarded validation/adoption: ```bash ./chatgpt_claudecode_workflow_release_control.sh \ --version v0.0.201 \ --tests-only \ --adopt-if-green \ --skip-docker-logs \ --prune-release-logs \ --release-log-keep 12 ```

