bash -lc cd /mnt/data/work_v208 && cat >> promptbranch_protocol/prompts/chatgpt_ask_contract.md <<'EOF' ## Locked MVP-F decisions - In protocol mode, the reply envelope is required; prose without the envelope is invalid. - Plain/manual `pb ask` may still use prose-only answers, but automation must ignore prose outside the envelope. - If multiple answers or multiple envelopes are present, Promptbranch must fail closed and require an explicit `answer_id`. - Artifact download is direct-URL-only for MVP. If no concrete `download.url` exists, report the candidate but do not download. - Artifact URLs are temporary. Include `answer_id` and `url_seen_at` when available so the host can re-resolve later. - Repair releases must be explicit with `release_type=repair`, `base_release`, `target_version`, and `repair_reason`. - MVP artifacts are ZIP-first. Non-ZIP outputs are diagnostics only until a separate baseline path is designed. EOF

