ocol-fresh-turn-timeout-seconds 60 \ --protocol-fresh-turn-poll-seconds 2 \ --json \ | tee .pb_profile/release_logs/v0.0.214/pb_ask_protocol_smoke.v0.0.214.json ``` ## Verdict ✅ Strengths — fixes the timeout-layer bug that prevented submit evidence from reaching the CLI. ⚠️ Weaknesses — still needs live proof that submit evidence is returned under real ChatGPT timeout conditions. 🔍 Unknowns — whether the next failure will classify as `assistant_response_timeout`, `ask_submit_not_triggered`, or `ask_submitted_dom_visible_backend_stale`. 🧩 Next step — validate/adopt `v0.0.214`, then rerun the protocol smoke.

